snippet.title: Gazzlers - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Gazzlers is an on-rails VR shooter where you build your ultimate weapon and use it to destroy the hordes of Gazzlers attacking your train. Shoot, block, and dodge your way across the lands of Ginkgo. It's coming soon to Meta Quest, Pico, PSVR2, and Steam VR.

#SummerOfGaming #VR
